{"tid":551172,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"美國在兩年前向港申請引渡一名疑犯 被港府拒絕","createTime":"2018-02-05T11:43:33.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-05T13:38:39.000Z","uid":5195,"like":48,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"a7af5f7ffebd40a69bd87894c3282146bfb76898","tid":551172,"uid":5195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-05T11:43:34.000Z","msg":"現在美國紐約羈押、民政事務局前局長何志平涉嫌賄賂非洲官員的案件，將在本港時間周二凌晨再在美國紐約提堂，屆時將處理他的保釋申請。美國司法部當地周日（2月4日）致函紐約地方法院法官，當中提到反對何志平保釋的理據，指何志平被控違反《海外反腐敗法》及洗黑錢等罪名，他面臨的所有罪名可判合共超過80年監禁。<br />\n<br />\n對於何志平一方指出，美國與香港有引渡協議，即使何獲保釋後返回香港，也會被捕及引渡回美，司法部指引述案例指，美國在兩年前向港申請引渡一名疑犯，卻被港府拒絕，認為成功引渡何志平回美的機會不會高。"},{"pid":"8da99b25132ea1304bb69901e7e0ec75722670c4","tid":551172,"uid":3773,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-05T12:03:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a79ad8241f12bf61bd2083b4bf4fd7cb0146cb4e","tid":551172,"uid":57705,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-05T12:03:54.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"6e171cdc140d2d790d532f4825e7bdd9e7fd7293","tid":551172,"uid":1067,"like":10,"dislike":1,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-05T12:05:00.000Z","msg":"呢次點都要支持美國"},{"pid":"5ee5065469b71bd401c30cdceb6def36c667dbba","tid":551172,"uid":35995,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"a79ad8241f12bf61bd2083b4bf4fd7cb0146cb4e","tid":551172,"uid":57705,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-05T12:03:54.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-05T12:05:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a4a7e04d4bc6aae6c2d4a20c8986c0ca5e16139e","tid":551172,"uid":34869,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-05T12:06:00.000Z","msg":"咁撚仆街有前科呀港共<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img